reamy pink gaming chair with soft adjustable bunny ears, ultra-comfy high-density cushion for fatigue-free gaming, and a sturdy yet adorable design that’s perfect for stylish gamer girls who love kawaii vibes!<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ebbdc6","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_E8QdKp":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/7_9d096501-649b-4524-b185-9e827072b8e7.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"end","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Bunny Ear Design","heading_tag":"h3","content":"<p>This bunny ear headband has a cute design and is made of plush fabric, with a combination of pink and white to make the bunny ear more kawaii, and the cute ears can be adjusted at any angle. Express your mood anytime.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ebbdc6","background_inner":"#f1d2d8","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_7qPXwb":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/6_161d1d15-ba8b-4c26-b058-19b018188ac9.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Less Fatigue Even After Long Hours of Sitting","heading_tag":"h3","content":"<p>AutoFull gaming chair have upgraded the cushion of this gamer chair according to customer demand, removing the side wings that squeeze the legs, making the seat spacious and free, suitable for both small and large body types. The shaped wadding seat cushion, comfortable rebound, even after a long time playing games, the hip is not easy to be sore.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ebbdc6","background_inner":"#f1d2d8","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_HjzdTf":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/4_cf3a1c38-d337-4d85-8e91-d27157ad27c7.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"end","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Game in Total Comfort","heading_tag":"h3","content":"<p>The AutoFull C2 wraps you in premium comfort with its contoured backrest, adjustable headrest and memory foam lumbar pillow – all working together to support your posture and keep fatigue at bay. No more soreness, just pure gaming joy!<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ebbdc6","background_inner":"#f1d2d8","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_JM6nRx":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_5f6b9766-bbaa-4fc4-88e2-2d868d8aa46b.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Premium Amway Leather – Luxury Meets Practicality","heading_tag":"h3","content":"<p>Crafted from the same high-end leather used in luxury goods, the AutoFull C2 offers a soft, supple feel while resisting stains and spills for effortless maintenance. Enjoy lasting elegance without the fuss.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#ebbdc6","background_inner":"#f1d2d8","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#1f1f1f","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_YmNcaj":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_9cf0b7da-9d1a-426e-942c-f850752a9e8f.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"end","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheadi